{"tid":245214,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[一人一信]Winning Eleven染紅？ 港澳台區旗國旗離奇消失","createTime":"2017-05-16T05:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T05:30:47.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75d9d364c72d84d4826e68fd12791f9cdd1ecb42","tid":245214,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:14:36.000Z","msg":"[一人一信]Winning Eleven染紅？ 港澳台區旗國旗離奇消失<br />\n<br />\n日本暢銷足球遊戲《Winning Eleven 2017》，係唔少港男由細玩到大嘅遊戲，可以算得上係香港人嘅集體回憶之一。隻game上年九月中推出嗰陣，仲新增本土元素嘅廣東話旁述，由足球評述員Keyman馬啟仁同前體育主播伍家謙配音。<br />\n<br />\n點知最近隻game疑似染紅，有玩家投訴上個月完成更新後，想創造球員嗰陣，發現香港同澳門區旗、台灣嘅中華民國國旗都離加消失。多年玩家、港大法律系碩士生兼「JR團隊」召集人盧俊宇，對此直言十分詫異。<br />\n<br />\n佢話一直玩開Winning，三支旗都存在，突然冇咗，難免令佢懷疑同政治有關，「你話我會唔會係政治敏感咗 當中係咪會驚得失一啲國家，或者得失中國呀甚至乎，因為咁啱淨係得中國有，澳門、台灣、香港冇，我覺得唔係咁容易解釋到。」<br />\n<br />\n盧坦言好失望，「我想做返個香港人，創造個香港籍嘅球員，嘩，原來我都冇自己既區旗睇到，咁其實仲有咩意思呢。」佢仲話唔少朋友幾乎罷玩。《壹》仔向遊戲製造商Konami查詢，但過咗幾日都未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170514/large/1494754994_4991.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170514%2Flarge%2F1494754994_4991.jpg&h=1348cc7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170514/large/1494754991_ce2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170514%2Flarge%2F1494754991_ce2f.jpg&h=217cb50a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170514/large/1494754997_677f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170514%2Flarge%2F1494754997_677f.jpg&h=7f06088b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170514/large/1494755000_f62a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170514%2Flarge%2F1494755000_f62a.jpg&h=a3178d21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盧俊宇懷疑港澳台三支旗消失，跟政治有關。"},{"pid":"1e708c906c378b78e588c3a0afe1b4c852f5bfda","tid":245214,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  趕走小島又奶共"},{"pid":"79f9f70c2378077f36b9b0a6ce4fff9d3b233d95","tid":245214,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:23:15.000Z","msg":"下個patch會將呢3個地方加返一支旗<br />\n叫五星紅旗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a1f1f3f5c2f977bae24655a13fd9ca7e0a299b","tid":245214,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:24:46.000Z","msg":"都冇人玩架啦"},{"pid":"d0358ca22394326c6bb2d0afe0d3518cfd0fb53d","tid":245214,"uid":98570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"抵佢冇人玩 細個果陣d人講起踢波game都諗起winning 宜家個個都玩fifa <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4253e2cdf4b8b3cd21061f517a88f13f89126d0f","tid":245214,"uid":7397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:27:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵佢冇人玩 細個果陣d人講起踢波game都諗起winning 宜家個個都玩fifa <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwinning前幾年做得太柒 加上fifa pro club仲ultimate team搶左好多客"},{"pid":"67c2d4a8482921d42a3e7bb51f986302161ec153","tid":245214,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抵佢冇人玩 細個果陣d人講起踢波game都諗起winning 宜家個個都玩fifa <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwinning前幾年做得太柒 加上fifa pro club仲ultimate team搶左好多客</blockquote><br />\n其實winning要轉型架啦,轉做RPG結合sandbox game可能係一條出路"}]}